definition: (of a smell) strong/peak season (of a crop)/(classifier for the ordinal number of a crop, in the context of multiple harvests)

sentences.english: The jet soared away into the distance.
sentences.chinese: 噴射機不停高飛進入遠方。

sentences.english: An airplane taxiing down the runway.
sentences.chinese: 我們看着噴射機沿跑道滑行。

sentences.english: That wealthy man has his own jet.
sentences.chinese: 那位富翁擁有自己的噴射機。

sentences.english: Tools – mainly plough, jetter, or rock cutter …
sentences.chinese: 多數用犁，噴射機，切巖機。

sentences.chinese: 噴射機的尖嘯聲侵犯了下午的平靜。

sentences.chinese: 一架鷹式噴射機在航空母艦上方盤旋。

sentences.english: We watched the jet plane taxiing down the runway.
sentences.chinese: 我們看着噴射機沿跑道滑行。
